T1  - When Employees Do Bad Things for Good Reasons: Examining Unethical Pro-Organizational Behaviors
AU  - Umphress, Elizabeth E.
AU  - Bingham, John B.
Y1  - 2010/09/15
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2011/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/orsc.1100.0559
